word_mean_info__list.difference: 社交上的正式用语，指无目的、礼节性的短暂拜访，访问者与被访问者之间一般只有社交或公务关系。
多指在计划之外或事先未打招呼的偶然、顺便访问。也可指参观。
常用词，含义广泛，既可指接受他人来访，又可指去访问他人。
正式用词，强调出于工作需要的访问，也指亲戚朋友间的看望。

bilingual.source: I am going to visit the museum.

bilingual.target: 他们参观了卡尔加里市。
记者们参观了魁北克市。
你还必须参观中央公园。

bilingual.source: I am not going to visit the museum.
bilingual.target: 我不打算去参观博物馆。

list.abstract: 英文单词。多用于参观、拜访；少数用于闲谈、聊天。

yingyinNormal.en: George's birthday treat is a visit to the museum dinosaur room.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治特别的生日礼物就是参观博物馆的恐龙。

yingyinNormal.en: You will visit the 1960s and give a report. Time travel.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们要参观二十世纪六十年代，并做出报告。穿越时空之旅。

yingyinNormal.en: Head to the historic Bastakia Quarter and visit the Sheikh Mohamed Centre for Cultural Understanding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 前往历史悠久的巴斯塔基亚区，参观穆罕默德酋长文化交流中心。

yingyinNormal.en: Maybe Goodie could visit the aquarium. What's the aquarium? The aquarium is a place where there are lots of fish.
yingyinNormal.zh: 也许金金可以去参观一下海洋馆。什么是海洋馆？海洋馆是有很多鱼的地方。

yingyinNormal.en: Perfect. Would you like to visit the new house? Yes, please. Daddy Pig is taking Peppa and George to see the house he's building.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真漂亮。你想参观一下新房子吗？是的，我想！猪爸爸带佩奇和乔治去看正在造的新房子。

yingyinNormal.en: Perfect. Would you like to visit the new house? Yes, please. Daddy Pig is taking Peppa and George to see the house he's building.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真漂亮。你想参观一下新房子吗？是的，我想！猪爸爸带佩奇和乔治去看正在造的新房子。

yingyinNormal.en: While my tour of the set of Game Of Thrones may have gained most attention, my visit to the Crumlin Road Gaol will remain vividly in my mind.
yingyinNormal.zh: 尽管我参观权力的游戏拍摄场地更吸引眼球，但克拉姆林道监狱之行却最是不能忘怀。

yingyinNormal.en: Perhaps it is time I pay them a visit. No.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是不是该会会他们。糟糕。

yingyinNormal.en: You don't have the resources to visit all 12. No.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们没有足够资源去探查十二个地方。对。

yingyinNormal.en: At dawn. A seamstress will pay you a visit shortly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 天一亮就处决，女裁缝很快就会来。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa and George's cousins are coming to visit today.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩奇和乔治的亲戚们今天要来拜访他们。

yingyinNormal.en: Serena's visit was short and apparently not very sweet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 瑟琳娜的拜访很仓促，而且非常不愉快。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm going to visit my grandma! I'm going to visit my grandma! Bravo, Peppa.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要去看我的奶奶了。太棒了，佩琪。

yingyinNormal.en: Papa Drac has to stay here to run the hotel. But he'll visit us. And we'll visit him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 德古公公得留在这管理酒店啊，但他会来探望我们，而我们也会探望他。

yingyinNormal.en: We can't do that. What if they come by for a visit?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们不能那么做，万一他们来看我们呢？

yingyinNormal.en: That's why Mama paid her visit. When? What did she want?
yingyinNormal.zh: 怪不得妈妈专程过来了一趟。什么时候？她有什么事？

yingyinNormal.en: You forged my signature? Did Mrs. Applebaum pay you a visit?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你伪造了我的签名? Applebaum夫人去见过你了吗?

yingyinNormal.en: It's a shame people can't visit there. That is the rule though.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不过不能去看望实在是太不爽了，没办法，规矩就是这样。

yingyinNormal.en: I invited my sister to visit so that we could fix our problems.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我邀请我妹妹来作客好解决我们之间的矛盾。

yingyinNormal.en: I suppose not. So you have nothing to fear if he pays us a visit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想不会。所以即便他来拜访我们你也不用怕。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: The zoology program attracts students for whom zoo <highlight>visits</highlight> were the crucial formative experience that led them to major in biological sciences.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 动物学项目吸引了一些学生，对他们来说，参观动物园是至关重要的成长经历，引导他们主修生物科学。

examination_example.sentence: Although good TV shows can help stir children's interest in conservation, they cannot replace the excitement of a zoo <highlight>visit</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 尽管好的电视节目有助于激发孩子们对自然保护的兴趣，但它们不能代替参观动物园的兴奋感。

examination_example.sentence: Suppose you have to cancel your travel plan and will not be able to <highlight>visit</highlight> Professor Smith.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 假设你不得不取消旅行计划，不能去拜访史密斯教授。

sense_info_list.en: to make an official visit to somebody, for example to perform checks or give advice

examination_example.sentence: Ever since America's colonial days, the Caribbean islands have been favorite places to <highlight>visit</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 自从美国殖民时期以来，加勒比群岛一直是人们最喜欢去的地方。

examination_example.sentence: It became fashionable for young aristocrats to <highlight>visit</highlight> Paris, Venice, Florence, and above all, Rome, as the culmination (终极) of their classical education.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 年轻贵族将访问巴黎、威尼斯、佛罗伦萨、尤其是罗马当做他们经典教育的终极事件，这已成为一种时尚。

examination_example.sentence: The essential place to <highlight>visit</highlight>, however, was Italy.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，最重要的游览地点是意大利。

examination_example.sentence: She <highlight>visited</highlight> soldiers' wives and mothers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 她拜访了士兵的妻子和母亲。

examination_example.sentence: If you can't get to the nursing home to <highlight>visit</highlight> grandma, you can use a telepresence robot to hang out with her.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果你不能去养老院看望奶奶，你可以用远程机器人来陪她。

examination_example.sentence: She would be able to <highlight>visit</highlight> more scenic spots.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 她可以参观更多的景点。

examination_example.sentence: You could <highlight>visit</highlight> Canberra, for example, or the Blue Mountains, or you could go for a drive down the Great Ocean Road.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 例如，你可以参观堪培拉或蓝山，或者你可以开车去大洋路。

examination_example.sentence: A friend recently took her mother to <highlight>visit</highlight> an expensive assisted living/nursing home near my town.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一位朋友最近带她妈妈去了我镇附近一家昂贵的养老院。

examination_example.sentence: In the show, Marie Kondo acts as a tiny garbage fairy for messy people, <highlight>visiting</highlight> their houses to share the wisdom of the "KonMari" method.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在节目中，近藤麻理惠(Marie Kondo)扮演了一个为邋遢的人服务的小垃圾仙女，她会到他们的房子里，与他们分享“近藤麻理惠”方法的智慧。

examination_example.sentence: But nobody greeted the daughter and mother when they arrived, though the <highlight>visit</highlight> has been planned; nobody introduced them to the other residents.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但是当他们到达时，没有人问候女儿和母亲，尽管参观已经计划好了；没有人把他们介绍给其他居民。

examination_example.sentence: New graduate students can learn who their advisers or temporary advisers are by <highlight>visiting</highlight> or emailing the departmental office and asking for the information.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 研究生新生可以通过访问系办公室或给系办公室发邮件询问他们的指导老师或临时指导老师的信息。

sense_info_list.zh: 登陆; 访问(网站; 网页)

examination_example.sentence: By 2016, nearly nine out of ten young women in the 12th grade said they <highlight>visited</highlight> social media sites every day.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 到2016年，12年级近十分之九的年轻女性表示，她们每天都会访问社交媒体网站。

examination_example.sentence_trans: Burchill正在酒店收拾行装，准备去拜访当地的一些朋友。

examination_example.sentence: My best friend worked there and I went to <highlight>visit</highlight> her.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我最好的朋友在那里工作，我去拜访了她。

examination_example.sentence: For more details, <highlight>visit</highlight> us at Unit 3 Park View Lane.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 欲了解更多详情，请访问我们在第3单元公园景观巷。

examination_example.sentence: Has it been a while since your last <highlight>visit</highlight> to a public library?

examination_example.sentence: Our final day, Friday, sees us <highlight>visit</highlight> central Paris and tour the main sights.

数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

word_family.mean: v. 访问；拜访；使某人遭受；参观；探望；视察；检查；巡视；闲聊；游览

sense_info_list.zh: 参观; 访问; 游览

examination_example.sentence: I'm going to <highlight>visit</highlight> Chengdu this summer holiday.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这个暑假我打算去成都旅游。

examination_example.sentence: No matter when you <highlight>visit</highlight> it, they will catch your eye.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 无论你什么时候去，他们都会吸引你的眼球。

examination_example.sentence: The tour includes a <highlight>visit</highlight> to the Disneyland, so you needn't pay for the tickets.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这次旅行包括参观迪斯尼乐园，所以你不必支付门票。

examination_example.sentence: I'm going to <highlight>visit</highlight> Mr. Li.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我打算去拜访李先生。

examination_example.sentence: I would also like to <highlight>visit</highlight> you at your home on the fourth of August.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我还想在8月4号去你家拜访你。

examination_example.sentence: Old Mr. Green doesn't feel lonely because some students <highlight>visit</highlight> him regularly.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 老格林先生并不感到孤独，因为有些学生经常来看望他。

examination_example.sentence: And you can also <highlight>visit</highlight> the websites your teachers suggest.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你还可以访问老师推荐的网站。

examination_example.sentence: Some websites don't allow kids under a certain age to <highlight>visit</highlight> them.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有些网站不允许特定年龄以下的孩子访问它们。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Visit</highlight> us on the website to place your order for a group in advance.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 访问我们的网站，提前为团队下订单。

sense_info_list.zh: 上门咨询专业人士; 专业人士上门服务

examination_example.sentence: We should <highlight>visit</highlight> a doctor if we have serious burns.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果烧伤严重，我们应该去看医生。

examination_example.sentence: In fact, among the 451 interviewed patients, 75% reported no pain at all during their <highlight>visits</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 事实上，在受访的451名患者中，75%的人表示在就诊过程中完全没有疼痛感。

examination_example.sentence: Brush your teeth at least twice a day, cut down sugary foods and drinks, and <highlight>visit</highlight> the dentist often.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 每天至少刷两次牙，减少含糖食物和饮料，经常看牙医。

word_usage.usage: 表示“拜访”，visit和call相对正式，drop in则是日常用语，有“顺便，不定期”的意味，see一般用于亲友间的访问。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 常用词，含义广泛，既可指接受他人来访，又可指去访问他人。
正式用词，强调出于工作需要的访问，也指亲戚朋友间的看望。
